                },
                "accordion_row_7YKQf4": {
                  "type": "_accordion-row",
                  "settings": {
                    "heading": "Social Media & PR Manager | Gold Coast, Australia",
                    "open_by_default": false,
                    "icon": "none",
                    "width": 20
                  },
                  "blocks": {
                    "text_cNxmzW": {
                      "type": "text",
                      "settings": {
                        "text": "<p><strong>The Role</strong></p><p>This is not a traditional marketing role. As our Content Director, you will define and drive the visual and editorial voice of Made With Love. You will create the content direction for all digital platforms, assist with concept development for brand campaigns, and direct a cross-functional creative team to deliver bold, emotional, and design-led storytelling.</p><p>This is a rare opportunity to shape the future of a brand that is redefining bridal fashion - blending cinematic beauty with and commercial relevance.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><p><strong>Brand Narrative and Creative Direction</strong></p><ul><li>Define and refine the visual identity and tone of voice across all brand channels</li><li>Contribute to concept development for seasonal campaigns, capsule launches, collaborations, and runway moments</li><li>Create all creative output, ensuring it reflects the evolving aesthetic and ambition of the brand</li></ul><p><strong>Content Strategy and Execution</strong></p><ul><li>Develop and own the brand’s content strategy across web, email, social, in-store, and emerging platforms</li><li>Create and contribute to the strategic content calendar that balances brand storytelling with commercial performance</li><li>Ensure all content is elevated, on-brand, and aligned with key business objectives</li></ul><p><strong>Social Media and Digital Content</strong></p><ul><li>Lead the creation, curation of all social content across Instagram, TikTok, Pinterest, and Facebook</li><li>Plan, shoot, and edit compelling, editorially-driven content tailored to each platform – from low-fi to elevated styles</li><li>Identify and leverage trends, sounds, and creative formats that extend reach, deepen engagement, and grow brand equity</li></ul><p><strong>Contribution and Collaboration</strong></p><ul><li>Collaborate with a growing in-house and freelance creative team, including designers, content creators, photographers, stylists, and editors</li><li>Collaborate closely with the design, digital, marketing, e-commerce, and retail teams to ensure seamless brand consistency across touchpoints</li><li>Source and manage external creative collaborators where required</li></ul><p><strong>Trend Leadership and Brand Innovation</strong></p><ul><li>Stay ahead of trends, ensuring the brand remains distinctive and aspirational</li><li>Identify and pitch creative partnerships, shoot concepts, or brand moments that push the brand forward</li></ul><p><strong>You Bring</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum 3 year’s experience in content, brand, or creative direction - ideally within fashion, beauty, lifestyle, or design-led brands</li><li>A strong portfolio showcasing creative leadership, storytelling, and brand development across digital and editorial platforms</li><li>Hands-on experience in shoot production, art direction, content creation, and social media execution</li><li>Proven ability to collaborate with and inspire a creative team in a fast-paced, highly visual business</li><li>A natural balance of conceptual thinking, editorial taste, and commercial awareness</li><li>Passion for high end fashion, and storytelling that resonates with a global audience</li></ul><p><strong>Why Join Us</strong></p><ul><li>Shape the creative direction of a globally recognised brand redefining bridal fashion</li><li>Lead work that is creatively fulfilling and commercially impactful</li><li>Join a collaborative and ambitious team where ideas are welcomed and originality is celebrated</li><li>Enjoy a culture of innovation, kindness, and real creative freedom</li></ul><p><strong>This is a career-defining opportunity for a content creator who wants to be a part of something meaningful and unforgettable.</strong></p><p><strong>Apply by:</strong><br/><br/><strong>Email</strong> | genea@madewithlovebridal.com</p><p><strong>SEEK </strong>| view listing <a href=\"https://www.seek.com.au/job/89011007?ref=hirer-jobs-list\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.seek.com.au/job/89011007?ref=hirer-jobs-list\">here</a>. </p>",
